@node Main "Hexit - Documentation"

                              'Hexit' 1.21

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Hexit' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} which displays two hexagonal shaped
boards filled with coloured tiles. One of these boards has a pattern
and the other is randomly shuffled. The @{" goal " link play} is to move the tiles
of the shuffled board in order to match the other board, in the least
amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

