@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Hexit" where you want
on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or
Libraries are needed. The only requirement is that your Workbench must
have at least 8 colours.

                             How to play?

  Playing the game is very simple: click on any tile surrounded by
6 other tiles. Each time you click on a tile, the game will rotate
the surrounding tiles clockwise by one position.

  Continue to move the tiles until the board matches the board on the
left. Try to complete the game with the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

OPTIONS

 -@{b}New Game@{ub}:                  Restarts the game (or Left Amiga + "N").

 -@{b}Small Board...Large Board@{ub}: Selects between the Small, Medium or Large
                       game board.

